Korg Inc. (株式会社コルグ Kabushiki-gaisha Korugu) Logo Korg Inc. (株式会社コルグ Kabushiki-gaisha Korugu), founded as Keio Electronic Laboratories, is a Japanese multinational corporation that manufactures electronic musical instruments, audio processors and guitar pedals, recording equipment, and electronic tuners. Under the Vox brand name, they also manufacture guitar amplifiers and electric guitars. Source
